  "page": "A Storm of Swords-Chapter 44",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Jaime VI</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_storm_of_swords\" title=\"A storm of swords\"><img alt=\"AStormOfSwords.jpg\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg/220px-AStormOfSwords.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbborder\" srcset=\"/images/2/24/AStormOfSwords.jpg 1.5x\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n500 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(35, 135, 75)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_37\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 37\">Jaime V</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_43\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 43\">Arya VIII</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\"><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Jaime VI</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_45\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 45\">Catelyn V</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n↓<br /><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_62\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 62\">Jaime VII</a></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Places_and_terms_mentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Places and terms mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#References_and_Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References and Notes</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_44&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Mustamirri_I_only_rescue_maidens.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5e/Mustamirri_I_only_rescue_maidens.jpg/200px-Mustamirri_I_only_rescue_maidens.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"311\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5e/Mustamirri_I_only_rescue_maidens.jpg/300px-Mustamirri_I_only_rescue_maidens.jpg 1.5x, /images/5/5e/Mustamirri_I_only_rescue_maidens.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Mustamirri_I_only_rescue_maidens.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>I only rescue maidens - by mustamirri ©</div></div></div>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a> has left <a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a> to the <a href=\"/index.php/Vargo_Hoat\" title=\"Vargo Hoat\">Goat</a>, but before marching for <a href=\"/index.php/The_Twins\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Twins\">the Twins</a> he told <a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime</a> to give his warm regards to <a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">his father</a>. Jaime responds, <i>\"So long as you give mine to <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a>.\"</i> \n</p><p>Jaime is now traveling for <a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a> under the protection of <a href=\"/index.php/Steelshanks_Walton\" title=\"Steelshanks Walton\">Steelshanks Walton</a> and a host of <a href=\"/index.php/Dreadfort\" title=\"Dreadfort\">Dreadfort</a> men. <a href=\"/index.php/Qyburn\" title=\"Qyburn\">Qyburn</a> tells him that Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Selwyn_Tarth\" title=\"Selwyn Tarth\">Selwyn</a> has promised Vargo Hoat 300 gold dragons for the safe return of <a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_of_Tarth\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brienne of Tarth\">his daughter</a>, but the goat wants more as he still believes there are sapphires in <a href=\"/index.php/Evenfall_Hall\" title=\"Evenfall Hall\">Evenfall Hall</a>. \n</p><p>One night, Jaime has a bizarre fever dream that he and Brienne are trapped in the dank caverns beneath <a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a>. He sees the shades of the other knights of the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> as well as Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar</a>, come to judge him for killing <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys</a>. After the fire of his sword goes out, Brienne’s continues to burn, defending him from the shades.\n</p><p>When Jaime awakens, he commands Walton to return to Harrenhal saying that he \"forgot something\". Back at Harrenhal, the goat’s men open the gates, and Jaime finds that Brienne has been tossed into the bear pit with only a tourney sword. \n</p><p>Vargo Hoat, with a bandage around his face from where Brienne bit off his ear, will not pull the woman up. Jaime jumps into the pit to save Brienne, and holds off the bear long enough for Walton’s men to fill it with quarrels. The <a href=\"/index.php/Brave_Companions\" title=\"Brave Companions\">Mummers</a> are unable to stop them because Steelshanks' escort of 200 men outnumbers them two to one. \n</p><p>Vargo asks Jaime to tell his father that he had been merciful, and the Kingslayer promises that the goat will receive his ransom. When Brienne asks him why he came back, Jaime responds that he had dreamed of her. \n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"Character_List_appearing/mentioned\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_44&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List appearing/mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Roose_Bolton\" title=\"Roose Bolton\">Roose Bolton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Vargo_Hoat\" title=\"Vargo Hoat\">Vargo Hoat</a> The Goat</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jaime_Lannister\" title=\"Jaime Lannister\">Jaime Lannister</a> Kingslayer</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Tywin_Lannister\" title=\"Tywin Lannister\">Tywin Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Steelshanks_Walton\" title=\"Steelshanks Walton\">Steelshanks Walton</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Qyburn\" title=\"Qyburn\">Qyburn</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rorge\" title=\"Rorge\">Rorge</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Three_Toes\" title=\"Three Toes\">Three Toes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Zollo\" title=\"Zollo\">Zollo</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Selwyn_Tarth\" title=\"Selwyn Tarth\">Selwyn Tarth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Brienne_of_Tarth\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Brienne of Tarth\">Brienne of Tarth</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaegar_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaegar Targaryen\">Rhaegar Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaella_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaella Targaryen\">Rhaella Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Cersei_Lannister\" title=\"Cersei Lannister\">Cersei Lannister</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Joffrey_Baratheon\" title=\"Joffrey Baratheon\">Joffrey Baratheon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Oswell_Whent\" title=\"Oswell Whent\">Oswell Whent</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jonothor_Darry\" title=\"Jonothor Darry\">Jonothor Darry</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lewyn_Martell\" title=\"Lewyn Martell\">Lewyn Martell</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Arthur_Dayne\" title=\"Arthur Dayne\">Arthur Dayne</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Gerold_Hightower\" title=\"Gerold Hightower\">Gerold Hightower</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Pia\" title=\"Pia\">Pia</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Places_and_terms_mentioned\">Places and terms mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_44&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Places and terms mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Harrenhal\" title=\"Harrenhal\">Harrenhal</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/The_Twins\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Twins\">The Twins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/King%27s_Landing\" title=\"King&#39;s Landing\">King's Landing</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Dreadfort\" title=\"Dreadfort\">Dreadfort</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Evenfall_Hall\" title=\"Evenfall Hall\">Evenfall Hall</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Casterly_Rock\" title=\"Casterly Rock\">Casterly Rock</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Brave_Companions\" title=\"Brave Companions\">Brave Companions</a> Mummers</li></ul>\n</div>\n<p><br />\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References_and_Notes\">References and Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_44&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References and Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>The synopsis was copied from Aol member vbkorik27 previously at<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external autonumber\" href=\"http://web.archive.